00:18:50.660 --> 00:18:53.700
The number of your retained
users that you convert.

00:18:53.810 --> 00:18:57.900
And the math really is crucial to whether
you can be successful in freemium.

00:18:57.980 --> 00:19:02.700
If you're building a niche product,
for example, that does not have a chance

00:19:02.760 --> 00:19:05.200
to be downloaded millions
and millions of times,

00:19:05.420 --> 00:19:09.360
you might see higher retention and
conversion and a higher average

00:19:09.400 --> 00:19:11.340
spend and the math can work out.

00:19:12.280 --> 00:19:15.930
In contrast, if you're building a product
that has potential to reach

00:19:16.350 --> 00:19:19.480
millions and millions of people,
you might see a lower conversion

00:19:19.550 --> 00:19:22.600
and a lower average spend,
