00:32:35.100 --> 00:32:38.980
You'll see them marketed through our over
400 retail locations around the globe

00:32:39.120 --> 00:32:42.010
and our thousands of channel partners.

00:32:42.500 --> 00:32:46.840
We spend a lot of energy marketing
apps on Apple.com or through the

00:32:46.850 --> 00:32:50.880
hundreds of millions of emails
