We want you to track your distribution
so we know how many codes you're

00:38:17.700 --> 00:38:19.610
putting through which channels.

00:38:19.610 --> 00:38:21.890
And then of course
you'll need our approval.

00:38:22.730 --> 00:38:26.120
So in order to gain this approval,
drop us an email at

00:38:26.120 --> 00:38:30.650
appstorecodes@apple.com and you'll
receive a template back from us that

00:38:30.670 --> 00:38:35.290
will ask you to fill out describing
your campaign and what you want to do.

00:38:35.730 --> 00:38:38.360
Once you receive our approval,
we'll send you an agreement.

00:38:38.500 --> 00:38:40.990
You guys sign the agreement,
you send it back to us,

00:38:41.050 --> 00:38:44.660
and then we'll provide you the
list of the unique 12-digit codes.

00:38:44.710 --> 00:38:48.370
What's great about this program is
that you can track the performance of

00:38:48.370 --> 00:38:52.380
it on a daily basis through the sales
and trends report you guys use today.

00:38:52.380 --> 00:38:55.450
So you'll know the effectiveness
quite quickly of these campaigns.

00:38:55.450 --> 00:38:56.900
So that's the App Store code program.

00:38:56.900 --> 00:38:58.820
The second program is iAd.

00:38:58.970 --> 00:39:02.030
iAd is Apple's digital
advertising platform.

00:39:02.180 --> 00:39:05.110
We know you work very hard
to create a beautiful app,

00:39:05.110 --> 00:39:09.640
and we don't want to see your experience
degraded with a poor ad experience.

00:39:09.690 --> 00:39:11.590
And that's where iAd comes in.

00:39:13.070 --> 00:39:16.050
iAd is now available in
14 countries worldwide,

00:39:16.440 --> 00:39:19.790
where we just launched in three
new countries this week in Taiwan,

00:39:19.790 --> 00:39:20.700
Hong Kong, and Ireland.

00:39:32.860 --> 00:39:32.860
Now, there's two aspects to iAd.

00:39:32.860 --> 00:39:32.860
There is the monetization side of iAd
and there's the promotion side of iAd.

00:39:32.860 --> 00:39:32.860
So let me begin by talking
about the monetization side.

00:39:33.620 --> 00:39:38.570
With iAd, you can monetize your app by
serving up iAds within your app.

00:39:38.720 --> 00:39:42.120
By doing so,
you'll receive a 70% revenue share

00:39:42.180 --> 00:39:43.860
for all the ads that you serve.

00:39:46.700 --> 00:39:49.460
Now the iAd platform is both
flexible and noncompetitive.

00:39:49.590 --> 00:39:53.140
And what I mean is that you can
go out and sell your own ads to

00:39:53.610 --> 00:39:57.460
render in addition to those that
are being presented with an iAd,

00:39:57.590 --> 00:40:00.700
but you also can block your competition
from showing up in your app.

00:40:01.260 --> 00:40:03.460
If you don't want certain apps
to be marketed in your app or

00:40:03.460 --> 00:40:06.700
certain brands to be marketed,
you have the ability to blacklist those.

00:40:06.700 --> 00:40:08.600
The ads that will be served to you,
you can be assured that

00:40:08.600 --> 00:40:12.030
they will be compelling,
rich media ads, as I said before,

00:40:12.030 --> 00:40:14.700
not to degrade your own app experience.

00:40:15.310 --> 00:40:18.700
And you can track the results in
real time through iTunes Connect.

00:40:18.700 --> 00:40:20.110
You can look at the
impressions being served,

00:40:20.110 --> 00:40:21.700
your clicks,
and the revenue being generated.

00:40:21.700 --> 00:40:23.700
So that's the monetization side.

00:40:24.110 --> 00:40:26.690
But in order to get started here,
there's only three things you need to do.

00:40:27.150 --> 00:40:31.700
First, go into iTunes Connect and
complete your iAd contract.

00:40:32.070 --> 00:40:35.690
Second,
enable the iAd framework within your app.

00:40:35.980 --> 00:40:37.680
And then third, you just submit your app
into the app review team.

00:40:37.690 --> 00:40:41.490
So let's move over to the promotion
side and how you can use iAd

00:40:41.490 --> 00:40:43.700
to drive downloads of your app.

00:40:44.390 --> 00:40:46.700
And with that, you use iAd Workbench.

00:40:46.700 --> 00:40:49.590
We announced iAd Workbench
at WWDC this last summer,

00:40:49.710 --> 00:40:53.700
