creation and management tool.

00:40:54.290 --> 00:40:57.400
When it was announced this summer,
it was only available in the US,

00:40:57.400 --> 00:40:59.960
but as of this week,
we now have iAd Workbench available

00:40:59.960 --> 00:41:01.700
in those same 14 countries.

00:41:02.470 --> 00:41:06.000
Again, there's now two sides of
the iAd Workbench product.

00:41:06.320 --> 00:41:09.690
There's the campaign creation
and there's the analytics.

00:41:10.090 --> 00:41:12.680
So let me explain to you quickly how to
create a campaign within iAd Workbench.

00:41:12.740 --> 00:41:16.700
create a campaign within IAD Workbench.

00:41:16.790 --> 00:41:18.260
There's only five steps.

00:41:18.430 --> 00:41:21.190
First, you need to select the app
that you want to promote,

00:41:21.190 --> 00:41:22.660
which is your app.

00:41:22.780 --> 00:41:25.110
Second, you need to select your audience.

00:41:25.220 --> 00:41:28.620
Now for the non-marketers in the room,
we make it very simple.

00:41:28.780 --> 00:41:32.450
You can select the automatic
targeting and the integration

00:41:32.450 --> 00:41:36.180
that iAd has with the App Store,
we will automatically find

00:41:36.230 --> 00:41:38.260
the best customers for you.

00:41:38.490 --> 00:41:41.150
Now for you marketers here in the room
