city or interest with various

00:41:48.280 --> 00:41:50.660
categories within the App Store.

00:41:50.660 --> 00:41:52.300
A number of different criteria.

00:41:54.100 --> 00:41:55.650
Next, you need to set your budget.

00:41:55.780 --> 00:41:58.620
Tell iAd how much you want
to spend over how many days.

00:41:58.720 --> 00:42:00.360
And then upload your creative.

00:42:00.360 --> 00:42:03.350
Again, if you're not the creative
type and you don't know how

00:42:03.450 --> 00:42:06.190
to create a great banner ad,
we provide four templates

00:42:06.190 --> 00:42:07.200
that you can use.

00:42:07.200 --> 00:42:11.520
And there's various iterations of that
with color and font that can make it

00:42:11.840 --> 00:42:14.320
look really unique to your own campaign.

00:42:14.320 --> 00:42:16.050
And then finally, submit it.

00:42:16.260 --> 00:42:18.770
You'll get response within
24 hours whether or not your

00:42:18.770 --> 00:42:21.450
campaign's been approved and
then you can begin to run it.

00:42:21.980 --> 00:42:25.340
Now, we provide a dashboard where you can
get a macro view of your account.

00:42:25.520 --> 00:42:28.500
You can monitor your campaigns
or initiate new ones.

00:42:28.500 --> 00:42:31.300
But you also can get detailed
statistics of your campaign.

00:42:31.300 --> 00:42:35.390
