00:42:35.390 --> 00:42:39.840
your impressions, your downloads,
your tap-through rates, your CPC,

00:42:39.840 --> 00:42:41.500
all this various stuff.

00:42:41.580 --> 00:42:44.710
And then you can also download
these metrics as a CSV from any

00:42:44.710 --> 00:42:48.440
